{
  "stem": "9878.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then this-- this-- this story is a story of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The same Czechs are wonderful people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they decided that we as people, surviving-- trying to survive-- are somehow getting into the gardens.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And some of them, real-- not farmers like myself, did damage to the tomatoes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They pulled the-- the-- the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they took all the potatoes with the-- out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And even the row, they didn't-- they didn't put back everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They even-- they did things that the farmers didn't like.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Of course, we were fighting for our lives-- for our survival.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So lo and behold, the same people I worked for-- the same people I spoke Czech with very well-- they decided to catch us and to threaten us, or beat us up, or give us over to the Germans because there is a rumor the Germans said they would  only kill two days, three days.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "From now on, they're not going to kill anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This was all deceit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The Germans used deceit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] they used the biggest psychiatrists to deceive our people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So all of a sudden, I go to look for food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I see kids, young kids, ran after me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they caught me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They caught more people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They took us to the starosta.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The starosta means the mayor of the village.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I was the only single person who understands Czechs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It's Slavic, but different than Polish, different than Russian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they keep on saying, the majority said, no let's beat them up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And let's tell them, listen, get the hell out of here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We don't want you to damage our gardens.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And some people who were not careful, they ripped the tomatoes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They did everything-- damage to the gardens.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
